#EXTM3U

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
#  CleanWatch M3U Playlist
#
#  HOW TO USE:
#  1. Replace the dood.la URLs with YOUR Doodstream links.
#  2. Replace tvg-logo URLs with your poster image URLs.
#  3. Upload this file to Google Drive and share as
#     "Anyone with the link - Viewer".
#  4. Copy the File ID from the share link and paste
#     it into CleanWatchProvider.kt line 27.
#
#  SECTIONS:
#    group-title="Movies"    → appears as Movies section
#    group-title="TV Shows"  → appears as TV Shows section
#    group-title="Channels"  → appears as Live Channels section
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════


